---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="bg-white px-5 py-24 text-slate-950">
  <div class="reveal mx-auto max-w-6xl overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(248,217,139,0.26),transparent_30%),linear-gradient(135deg,#07152f,#1e3a8a)] p-8 text-white shadow-2xl shadow-canaa-950/20 sm:p-12 lg:p-16">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto]">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.26em] text-gold-300">Proximo passo</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Sua primeira visita pode ser simples, acolhedora e bem orientada.</h2>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-200">Envie seus dados e receba informacoes sobre horarios, recepcao, criancas, ministerios e como chegar.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="#contato" data-analytics="final_cta" class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-gold-300 px-7 py-4 text-base font-extrabold text-canaa-950 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-white">
        Quero falar com a equipe
        <Icon name="arrow" class="h-5 w-5 transition group-hover:translate-x-1" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
